{"tid":800812,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"龜缸頂濾求教學","createTime":"2018-08-31T07:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T18:25:55.000Z","uid":78377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a209313cd066165c8166e52b5b4c7333a1714cc9","tid":800812,"uid":78377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T07:10:36.000Z","msg":"想整濾水<br />\n追post講話可以用潛水泵加頂濾<br />\n但我係一D相關知識都無<br />\n所以來求教學<br />\n<br />\n我本身用緊日本城膠箱<br />\n洗唔洗一定轉缸先裝到濾？"},{"pid":"4f5abfce882bb69e34963f6c1ab45fd1732715c1","tid":800812,"uid":78377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T07:14:05.000Z","msg":"如果可以 <br />\n請影一影setup上來參考下<br />\n<br />\n另外想知有冇靜音既頂濾加潛水泵？"},{"pid":"3e337e74ead950bcefcda4a8c94c6876505acefa","tid":800812,"uid":78377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T15:33:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66b6683f81da6e79a2c88e50c1244d30d4cea9af","tid":800812,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e337e74ead950bcefcda4a8c94c6876505acefa","tid":800812,"uid":78377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T15:33:24.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T16:19:43.000Z","msg":"點解唔索性quote嗰啲巴打嚟問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59c325d9e95470a3e45ea48397640d604c3d006f","tid":800812,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a209313cd066165c8166e52b5b4c7333a1714cc9","tid":800812,"uid":78377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T07:10:36.000Z","msg":"想整濾水<br />\n追post講話可以用潛水泵加頂濾<br />\n但我係一D相關知識都無<br />\n所以來求教學<br />\n<br />\n我本身用緊日本城膠箱<br />\n洗唔洗一定轉缸先裝到濾？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T18:25:55.000Z","msg":"用膠箱都可以<br />\n睇你放個到有冇空間 怕唔怕嘈可以有唔同setting<br />\n我自己用膠缸係龜缸隔離做過濾<br />\n一條喉用虹吸抽水去濾缸<br />\n一條喉加泵，將濾缸嘅水抽返過龜缸<br />\n呢個setting好處係我會控制到濾缸水位，唔怕滿到漏出黎，同埋用料好平，水keep到清<br />\n你頂濾要留意水流返落黎嘅噪音問題"}]}